     "{\"template\":\"intro\",\"texts\":[\"If your plans change you can apply to make certain amendments to a Low Emission Zone (LEZ) charge, or for a refund for the days you are not going to use.\"],\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"Charge amendments\"}",
     "You can ask to change the start date of a LEZ charge, the vehicle, or both the start date and vehicle.",
     "You can only change the start date of a charge if it starts today or on a future date, You can't amend charges for any dates in the past.",
     "To apply for an amendment you willÂ need the:",
     "{\"template\":\"bulletlist\",\"items\":[\"Number plate (Vehicle Registration Mark)\",\"Receipt number and the charge start date of the charge you want to amend\"]}",
     "{\"template\":\"start-row\",\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"end-row\",\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"Refunds\"}",
     "If you decide not to use your vehicle in the LEZ you can request a refund of the charge as long as you apply either on the day of travel or before it.",
     "We don't refund charges for dates in the past.",
     "To request a refund you will need the:",
     "{\"template\":\"bulletlist\",\"items\":[\"Number plate (Vehicle Registration Mark)\",\"Receipt number and charge start date for the charge you want refunded\"]}",
